{"type":"article","id":5631,"title":"“中国叔叔要把我的11岁女儿带去过夜”","uid":8354,"topics":[1,552,163,330,1454],"contents":"<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFdPedZUcAAKjW2?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFdPedZUcAAKjW2?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFdPedZUcAAKjW2?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<b>集中营幸存者Zumret Dawut: &quot;照片里这名20岁汉族男性是政府为我们家指定的'亲戚'。他数次提出要带我11岁女儿独自去他家过夜，还保证第二天早上送到学校。我都婉言谢绝，然后又怕当局会以这为借口把我再次关进我曾被囚过两个多月的地狱般的集中营。我吓得彻夜哭泣和祷告，祈求真主保佑我和家人。&quot;</b><br>\n<br>\n推号<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Uyghurspeaker\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@Uyghurspeaker</a>&nbsp;转载自<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=168897434266878&amp;id=100034398679054&amp;ref=content_filter\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">脸书</a>。","date":"2019-09-27","agreeCount":8,"discussionCount":0}